{"tha-ap547:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap547:0.2":"Bhaddiyavagga ","tha-ap547:0.3":"Nandakattheraapadana ","tha-ap547:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap547:1.2":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","tha-ap547:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap547:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","tha-ap547:2.1":"Hitaya sabbasattanam, ","tha-ap547:2.2":"sukhaya vadatam varo; ","tha-ap547:2.3":"Atthaya purisajanno, ","tha-ap547:2.4":"patipanno sadevake. ","tha-ap547:3.1":"Yasaggapatto sirima, ","tha-ap547:3.2":"kittivannabhato jino; ","tha-ap547:3.3":"Pujito sabbalokassa, ","tha-ap547:3.4":"disa sabbasu vissuto. ","tha-ap547:4.1":"Uttinnavicikiccho so, ","tha-ap547:4.2":"vitivattakathankatho; ","tha-ap547:4.3":"Paripunnamanasankappo, ","tha-ap547:4.4":"patto sambodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap547:5.1":"Anuppannassa maggassa, ","tha-ap547:5.2":"uppadeta naruttamo; ","tha-ap547:5.3":"Anakkhatanca akkhasi, ","tha-ap547:5.4":"asanjatanca sanjani. ","tha-ap547:6.1":"Maggannu maggavidu ca, ","tha-ap547:6.2":"maggakkhayi narasabho; ","tha-ap547:6.3":"Maggassa kusalo sattha, ","tha-ap547:6.4":"sarathinam varuttamo. ","tha-ap547:7.1":"Tada mahakaruniko, ","tha-ap547:7.2":"dhammam desesi nayako; ","tha-ap547:7.3":"Nimugge kamapankamhi, ","tha-ap547:7.4":"samuddharati panine. ","tha-ap547:8.1":"Bhikkhuninam ovadane, ","tha-ap547:8.2":"savakam setthasammatam; ","tha-ap547:8.3":"Vannayam etadaggamhi, ","tha-ap547:8.4":"pannapesi mahamuni. ","tha-ap547:9.1":"Tam sutvaham pamudito, ","tha-ap547:9.2":"nimantetva tathagatam; ","tha-ap547:9.3":"Bhojayitva sasangham tam, ","tha-ap547:9.4":"patthayim thanamuttamam. ","tha-ap547:10.1":"Tada pamudito natho, ","tha-ap547:10.2":"mam avoca mahaisi; ","tha-ap547:10.3":"‘Sukhi bhavassu dighavu, ","tha-ap547:10.4":"lacchase tam manoratham. ","tha-ap547:11.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap547:11.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap547:11.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap547:11.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap547:12.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap547:12.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap547:12.3":"Nandako nama namena, ","tha-ap547:12.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap547:13.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap547:13.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap547:13.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap547:13.4":"tavatimsupago aham. ","tha-ap547:14.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","tha-ap547:14.2":"jato setthikule aham; ","tha-ap547:14.3":"Savatthiyam pure vare, ","tha-ap547:14.4":"iddhe phite mahaddhane. ","tha-ap547:15.1":"Purappavese sugatam, ","tha-ap547:15.2":"disva vimhitamanaso; ","tha-ap547:15.3":"Jetaramapatiggahe, ","tha-ap547:15.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap547:16.1":"Nacireneva kalena, ","tha-ap547:16.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","tha-ap547:16.3":"Tatoham tinnasamsaro, ","tha-ap547:16.4":"sasito sabbadassina. ","tha-ap547:17.1":"Bhikkhuninam dhammakatham, ","tha-ap547:17.2":"patipucchakarim aham; ","tha-ap547:17.3":"Sasita ta maya sabba, ","tha-ap547:17.4":"abhavimsu anasava. ","tha-ap547:18.1":"Satani pancanunani, ","tha-ap547:18.2":"tada tuttho mahahito; ","tha-ap547:18.3":"Bhikkhuninam ovadatam, ","tha-ap547:18.4":"aggatthane thapesi mam. ","tha-ap547:19.1":"Satasahasse katam kammam, ","tha-ap547:19.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap547:19.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap547:19.4":"kilese jhapayim mama. ","tha-ap547:20.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap547:20.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap547:20.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap547:21.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap547:21.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap547:21.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap547:22.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap547:22.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap547:22.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap547:23.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nandako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap547:24.1":"Nandakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}